  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >About the game:</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>-- Construction --</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game, you can collect resources and use them to build your castle and house to resist the enemy's attack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/a6d417f01f4c64e31070cd5ed5544124.poster.avif?t=1748216418\" width=568 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/a6d417f01f4c64e31070cd5ed5544124.webm?t=1748216418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/a6d417f01f4c64e31070cd5ed5544124.mp4?t=1748216418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>-- Battle --</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are enemy patrols every night, so be ready to pick up your weapons to meet the enemy. Defeat the enemy and retrieve the architectural drawings they have stolen to unlock more buildings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/ee9eff081dc52f4442f53e8077b2da0a.poster.avif?t=1748216418\" width=568 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/ee9eff081dc52f4442f53e8077b2da0a.webm?t=1748216418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/ee9eff081dc52f4442f53e8077b2da0a.mp4?t=1748216418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>-- Capture enemies --</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yes, beyond combat, we can capture foes and repurpose them. Additionally, we can recruit other creatures to fight alongside us.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/ec938e4e4e394dad932a9509e9b399ec.poster.avif?t=1748216418\" width=568 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/ec938e4e4e394dad932a9509e9b399ec.webm?t=1748216418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/ec938e4e4e394dad932a9509e9b399ec.mp4?t=1748216418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>-- Teamwork --</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can give orders to other villagers, let them play to their strengths and better cooperate with your actions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/53be8e7f7f08bdd4e2f41f3ee9d52ba6.poster.avif?t=1748216418\" width=568 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/53be8e7f7f08bdd4e2f41f3ee9d52ba6.webm?t=1748216418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/53be8e7f7f08bdd4e2f41f3ee9d52ba6.mp4?t=1748216418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>-- Day and night system --</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How to arrange your time every day and how to make decisions is entirely up to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/c087a45da1118babbe07f07bcb08b35a.poster.avif?t=1748216418\" width=568 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/c087a45da1118babbe07f07bcb08b35a.webm?t=1748216418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/c087a45da1118babbe07f07bcb08b35a.mp4?t=1748216418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect, fight, explore, and build! Nothing is impossible in this dynamic adventure game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up your tools and set off! Fight the enemy and survive in the dark. Collect resources to create everything you need for your world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Finally defeat the dark forces.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But beware, there are many challenges waiting for you... Can you handle the mission?</p>",
