--</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How to arrange your time every day and how to make decisions is entirely up to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/c087a45da1118babbe07f07bcb08b35a.poster.avif?t=1748216418\" width=568 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/c087a45da1118babbe07f07bcb08b35a.webm?t=1748216418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/c087a45da1118babbe07f07bcb08b35a.mp4?t=1748216418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect, fight, explore, and build! Nothing is impossible in this dynamic adventure game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up your tools and set off! Fight the enemy and survive in the dark. Collect resources to create everything you need for your world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Finally defeat the dark forces.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But beware, there are many challenges waiting for you... Can you handle the mission?</p>",
